Geedka heedu wuxuu xubin ka yahay dhirta [[cows]]leyda ah. Geedkani isaga ayaa isbacarimiya, wuxuuna leeyahay jiinisyo ka kooban [[14|14 koromosoom]]. Noocyada geedaha ay ka soo tafiirantay heedu waxay si xoogan uga baxaan xoogaga iyo banaanada deegaanda [[nafaqo|carada nafaqada leh]] ee Galbeedka Aasiya iyo Koonfurbari Afrika.<ref name = Zohary>{{cite book|last=Zohary|first=Daniel|author2=Maria Hopf|title=Domestication of Plants in the Old World: The Origin and Spread of Cultivated Plants in West Asia, Europe, and the Nile Valley |url=http://books.google.com/?id=C1H6_XWJS_gC&pg=PA59&vq=barley&dq=Domestication+of+Plants+in+the+Old+World:+The+Origin+and+Spread+of+Cultivated+Plants+in+West+Asia,+Europe,+and+the+Nile+Valley|edition=3rd |year=2000|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=0-19-850357-1|pages= 59–69}}</ref> 

